{"tid":965463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十個黑警喺公民廣場包圍標語伯伯同埋雷玉蓮","createTime":"2019-01-02T05:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T09:48:44.000Z","uid":47359,"like":59,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00f6b548f35c6fa16c0c4ae39ac0011a5354ab52","tid":965463,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"心諗呢個年紀應該安享晚年<br />\n但都拋個身出嚟抗衡啲黑警<br />\n冒住受傷（伯伯真係俾人推跌，我都驚佢俾人壓傷）同被捕嘅風險堅持理念<br />\n如果我唔去護航我重係人嚟嘅？<br />\n黑警陰陰咀笑住整爛伯伯個標語個樣我記得好清楚<br />\n於是我同其他獨派朋友衝前保護佢哋<br />\n<br />\n最後想講<br />\n呢啲看似和理非嘅遊行<br />\n其實黑警都不斷武力打壓中<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每次遊行都需要大家團結出嚟</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c372b4ac0463a2683fe18459806750dbad01245b","tid":965463,"uid":47359,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"每次遊行都需要大家團結出嚟！！！"},{"pid":"583f13b5c3ef08bea47e198c89e4f8f0eaa6715a","tid":965463,"uid":47359,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"黑警選擇性打壓<br />\n泛民講野籌款冇事<br />\n獨派行路講句野都要拍低"},{"pid":"6b948a631a611602ed7a007557cc71b3533eb2a4","tid":965463,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"a8d5649835a760bafae70e3ceb5c9cfa69466226","tid":965463,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:56:27.000Z","msg":"阿伯都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330f618888e569479f453e9884f107aae4d050dd","tid":965463,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d5649835a760bafae70e3ceb5c9cfa69466226","tid":965463,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:56:27.000Z","msg":"阿伯都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face